{"id": "art-22", "label": "Art. 22", "title": "Art. 22: Cancelaria Prim-Ministrului", "slug": "art-22", "content": "<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:4.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><b style='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'><span style='color:\nblack'>Art. 22: Cancelaria Prim-Ministrului </span></b></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_2023625614\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1733\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_2023625614\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(1)Cancelaria Prim-Ministrului este structur&#259; cu\npersonalitate juridic&#259;, în subordinea prim-ministrului,\nfinan&#355;at&#259; prin bugetul Secretariatului General al Guvernului.</span><br\nstyle='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='color:black'>(2)Cancelaria Prim-Ministrului este\ncondus&#259; de &#351;eful Cancelariei Prim-Ministrului, care are rang de\nministru, numit &#351;i eliberat din func&#355;ie prin decizie a\nprim-ministrului.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1888957192\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1732\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1888957192\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(2<sup>1</sup>)În exercitarea atribu&#355;iilor care îi\nrevin, &#351;eful Cancelariei Prim-Ministrului emite ordine &#351;i\ninstruc&#355;iuni, în condi&#355;iile legii.</span><br style='mso-special-character:\nline-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_2054185091\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1731\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_2054185091\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(3)Atribu&#355;iile, organizarea &#351;i func&#355;ionarea,\nstructura organizatoric&#259; &#351;i num&#259;rul maxim de posturi ale\nCancelariei Prim-Ministrului se stabilesc prin hot&#259;râre a Guvernului.</span><br\nstyle='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_676523406\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1730\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_676523406\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(4)Personalul din cadrul Cancelariei Prim-Ministrului este\nformat din personal contractual &#351;i func&#355;ionari publici.</span><br\nstyle='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='color:black'>(5)În cadrul Cancelariei\nPrim-Ministrului î&#351;i desf&#259;&#351;oar&#259; activitatea unul sau mai\nmul&#355;i secretari de stat &#351;i consilieri de stat, precum &#351;i\ndirectorul de cabinet al prim-ministrului, cu rang de secretar de stat, numi&#355;i,\nrespectiv elibera&#355;i din func&#355;ie prin decizie a prim-ministrului.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='color:black'>(6)Prin hot&#259;râre a Guvernului\nse stabilesc institu&#355;iile publice &#351;i organele de specialitate ale\nadministra&#355;iei publice centrale coordonate de prim-ministru, prin\nCancelaria Prim-Ministrului.</span></p>"}